Developer Terms of Use
des:
If you're pregnant, you probably know some of the basic pregnancy advice about taking care of yourself and the baby: don't smoke or be around secondhand smoke, don't drink, and get your rest. 

Is it safe to exercise? 
Can I eat Fish? 

Ask really simple daily questions and get an answer at your fingertips. 


To enable the skill, simply say "Alexa, open Pregnancy Tips.”
To quit, just say "Alexa, quit" anytime during the session.

This skill does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
